<section sectnbr = "5E">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "05">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A5506001" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
TCM Learning Value Initialization
</title>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
If TCM learning value initialization is not performed after one of the following works has been performed, there is a possibility that the vehicle will not be able to move.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Be sure to perform TCM learning value initialization whenever one of the following works has been performed:
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
TCM is replaced.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CVT assembly is replaced.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention4>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Select learning procedure from table below.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
*: When replacing the TCM first, perform the initialization procedure [C].
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "3" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.063in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.396in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "1.000in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
TCM
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
CVT assembly
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Learning Procedure
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
When replacing with new one
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Not replace
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
[A]
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
When replacing with new one or used one
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
[A] or [C]*
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Not replace
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
When replacing with new one or used one
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
[B]
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
When replacing with used one
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Not replace
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
[C]
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
When replacing with new one or used one
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Perform selected initialization procedure as follows.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
Initialization procedure [A]:
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
With ignition OFF and shift select lever to P range, connect SUZUKI scan tool to DLC (1).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5E005">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "NNNNN-00024">
SUZUKI scan tool (SUZUKI-SDT)
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A510002.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "67.502mm" ver = "01" gw = "159" gh = "175"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Set ignition ON and leave ignition in ON for 10 sec.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Check that transmission warning light does not come on and DTC is not detected in TCM.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Perform 
<intxref refid = "AENBP70A5506042">Slope Sensor Calibration</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
Initialization procedure [B]:
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Perform step a) and b) of Initialization procedure [A].
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Select “Learning Value Initialization” function under “Utility” mode on SUZUKI scan tool, and follow the instructions displayed on SUZUKI scan tool.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
Initialization procedure [C]:
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Perform Initialization procedure [B].
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
After performing “TCM Learning Value Initialization”, Perform 
<intxref refid = "AENBP70A5506042">Slope Sensor Calibration</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s2>
</s1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
